Title: Visit Name
Description: Visit name: M - in months, SC - screening visit, LOG - records without visit; #2 or #3 define repated records at the same visit or repeated visit

Title: Visit Month
Description: Numeric visit in months; for visits prior baseline -1, -2 is an order of screening visits

Title: DaTSCAN Date
Description: Number of months after baseline visit at which DaTSCAN scan occurred; negative values indicate scan occurred before baseline

Title: DaTSCAN Visual Interpretation Report
Description: DaTSCAN SPECT Visual Interpretation Assessment Report
